docs.text: Welcome to MkDocs For full documentation visit mkdocs.org . Commands mkdocs new [dir-name] - Create a new project. mkdocs serve - Start the live-reloading docs server. mkdocs build - Build the documentation site. mkdocs -h - Print help message and exit. docs.text: About Hello! This is the documentation for the pygwalker package. It is a Python package that allows you to create interactive visualizations of your data using a simple and intuitive API. The package is designed to be easy to use and flexible, allowing you to create a wide variety of visualizations with minimal effort. test
